From: Peter Xu <peterx@redhat.com>
Date: Tue, 5 Mar 2024 12:37:48 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] mm/treewide: replace pud_large() with pud_leaf()
References: bsc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 6.8.5
Git-commit: 0a845e0f6348ccfa2dcc8c450ffd1c9ffe8c4add

[ Upstream commit 0a845e0f6348ccfa2dcc8c450ffd1c9ffe8c4add ]

pud_large() is always defined as pud_leaf().  Merge their usages.  Chose
pud_leaf() because pud_leaf() is a global API, while pud_large() is not.

